   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>So, they, forcing their father, joined the ranks of the army of the sons of Herakles. And they embarked for sea and brought over the Peloponnesian army against them. In it was Orestes' son Tisamenos. Temenos the eldest of the Herakleidai said, in drawing up his army, that he would hand over the kingdom to that one of his sons who gained most distinction in the battle. The result of the battle was in the Heraklids' favour and Archelaos the eldest was judged the most distinguished ... Temenidai ...</ab>
         </div>
